title: Katsuki Umezu
text:
is a <a href="Japanese%20people">Japanese</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="Gamba%20Osaka">Gamba Osaka</a>.
Career.
Katsuki Umezu joined <a href="Gamba%20Osaka">Gamba Osaka</a> in 2016. On, he debuted in <a href="J3%20League">J3 League</a> (v <a href="AC%20Nagano%20Parceiro">AC Nagano Parceiro</a>).
Last Updated: 3 December 2017
